							<div id="post-53322" class="post post-53322 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-education category-government category-internet tag-charter-schools tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-e-learning tag-education-reform tag-online-education tag-online-schools tag-school-choice tag-student-performance tag-technology tag-virtual-schools">
